== Data Usage Notice ==

MLB data accessed through the MLB Stats API (statsapi.mlb.com) is subject to
MLB Advanced Media's terms of use and is restricted to individual,
non-commercial, non-bulk use. Commercial use or bulk access requires prior
written authorization from MLB Advanced Media.
See: http://gdx.mlb.com/components/copyright.txt
